===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} [[νυμφε]], ''water [[nymph]]'', via {{L.}} [[lympha]], ''water nymph''

===Noun===
'''lymph'''
# {{physiology}} A colourless, watery, bodily fluid carried by the [[lymphatic system]], that consists mainly of [[white blood cell]]s.

